					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I think MIDI files are not the best format for final distribution of music, unless what you are intending to distribute is the sequence of notes rather than the sounds, anyways (although it can be used during your work; also, of course you can distribute both files, if you want to distribute both the sounds and the notes!). However, MIDI can be use for many things, not only music.</div>

					
